                p.about-txt A local staple, Opium Restaurant prides itself on using the freshest natural ingredients from the farm to table. Established in 2017 by Chef Mekbib Kassa, Opium Restaurant specializes in American Tex-Mex dishes. Located in Bole on the ground ﬂoor of Rakan Building, Opium Restaurant is known for having the best burritos in Addis Ababa. The menu assortment also offers delicious toasted sandwiches and flame grilled juicy burgers. Craving a Tex-Mex Breakfast? Try the Chef’s recommended Huevos Rancheros or grab a breakfast burrito on the go!
